<p>The <code>context</code> mode does not show the default icons(copy,paste) on <code>lollipop</code> , it works or other versions. Following is the theme unser <code>values-21</code></p>  <pre><code>&lt;resources&gt;      &lt;style name="BaseTheme.MainTheme"&gt;         &lt;item name="android:windowDrawsSystemBarBackgrounds"&gt;true&lt;/item&gt;         &lt;item name="android:fitsSystemWindows"&gt;true&lt;/item&gt;         &lt;item name="android:statusBarColor"&gt;@color/grey&lt;/item&gt;     &lt;/style&gt;      &lt;style name="BaseTheme.MainTheme.WithNavDrawer"&gt;         &lt;item name="android:windowDrawsSystemBarBackgrounds"&gt;true&lt;/item&gt;         &lt;item name="android:windowActionModeOverlay"&gt;true&lt;/item&gt;         &lt;item name="android:statusBarColor"&gt;@color/grey&lt;/item&gt;     &lt;/style&gt;  &lt;/resources&gt; </code></pre>  <p><a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/DletZ.png" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/DletZ.png" alt="enter image description here"></a></p>